Sunshine Pvt. ITI College
Syllabus: PGDCA (Post Graduate Diploma in Computer Application) - 1 Year
University: MCU Bhopal

Semester 1:
- Fundamentals of Computers & IT
- Operating Systems (DOS, Windows, Linux)
- PC Packages (MS Office)
- Database Management Systems (MS Access / FoxPro)

Semester 2:
- System Analysis and Design
- Web Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)
- Programming in C++ / Java / Python
- Financial Accounting with Tally
- Major Project Work
